      <div class="msgHeaderFrame" id="m1288496151160319914">
        
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-10-30 21:35:51   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1288496151160319914" id="quote-1288496151160319914" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1288496151160319914" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=152&amp;mid=1286816918312899321&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1288496151160319914&amp;page=4" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> 
